nodes.text: You Are Not a Jedi Yet

You Are Not a Jedi Yet is an article written by J.D. Wiker as a tie in to the Living Force campaign. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on September 11, 2003 and offered advice for roleplayers of Jedi characters on how to more accurately portray their characters, as well as advice for gamemasters on how to manage Jedi characters.
